{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/mih/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2018-09-28T17:37:55Z", "updated_at": "2021-09-02T13:12:02Z", "closed_at": "2021-09-02T13:12:02Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Whenever `git annex info` exposes all the remote parameters within `info` output:\r\n\r\n```shell\r\n$> git annex info s3-PUBLIC       \r\nuuid: deaa691f-c824-4416-9bf8-a94a47dd31b5\r\ndescription: [s3-PUBLIC]\r\nremote: s3-PUBLIC\r\ntrust: untrusted\r\ncost: 200.0\r\ntype: S3\r\ncreds: not available\r\nbucket: openneuro.org\r\nendpoint: s3.amazonaws.com\r\nport: 80\r\nstorage class: STANDARD\r\npartsize: 1.07 gigabytes\r\npublic: no\r\nversioning: no\r\nencryption: none\r\nchunking: none\r\nexport: yes\r\nremote annex keys: 136\r\nremote annex size: 2.42 gigabytes (+ 56 unknown size)\r\n```\r\nwe do not provide them anyhow, although they (e.g. all those `export`, `publicurl`, etc) could be very well to know:\r\n```shell\r\n$> datalad -f json_pp siblings -s s3-PUBLIC\r\n{\r\n  \"action\": \"query-sibling\",\r\n  \"annex-description\": \"[s3-PUBLIC]\",\r\n  \"annex-s3\": \"true\",\r\n  \"annex-uuid\": \"deaa691f-c824-4416-9bf8-a94a47dd31b5\",\r\n  \"name\": \"s3-PUBLIC\",\r\n  \"path\": \"/tmp/ds000001\",\r\n  \"refds\": \"/tmp/ds000001\",\r\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\r\n  \"type\": \"sibling\"\r\n}\r\n\r\n$> datalad -f json_pp siblings -s s3-PUBLIC configure\r\n{\r\n  \"action\": \"configure-sibling\",\r\n  \"annex-description\": \"[s3-PUBLIC]\",\r\n  \"annex-ignore\": \"false\",\r\n  \"annex-s3\": \"true\",\r\n  \"annex-uuid\": \"deaa691f-c824-4416-9bf8-a94a47dd31b5\",\r\n  \"fetch\": \"+refs/heads/*:refs/remotes/s3-PUBLIC/*\",\r\n  \"name\": \"s3-PUBLIC\",\r\n  \"path\": \"/tmp/ds000001\",\r\n  \"refds\": \"/tmp/ds000001\",\r\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\r\n  \"type\": \"sibling\"\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "mih", "id":